title: The New Tsars 02 - Blast Shock (2005) (Scanlation) cbr
description:
Pursued by a corrupt military, weapons inspector Yuri Vladimir is abandoned by his superiors. Then his situation is even more complicated when he's framed for murdering a priest, before accidentally killing a civilian, and having to flee with a female "hostage" to ensure his escape. Meanwhile, one of the Chechen terrorists who purchased nuclear warheads from a Russian minister negotiates his confession to the British government...
But all is not what it seems...

enjoy
